# In Support of a Hero

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:kino, "~> 0.18.0"}
])
```

## Introduction

This notebook is intended for verifying the calculated distances of sequences of cities in **Quest 3** of the C exercises.

**Instructions:** Go to the [user interface](#user-interface) section, evaluate the first cell, and enter your sequence of cities. Then evaluate the rest of the cells.

## Config

No need to touch the config.

```elixir
default_sequence =
  """
  Esbjerg
  Herning
  Silkeborg
  Viborg
  Aalborg
  Randers
  Århus
  Helsingør
  København
  Roskilde
  Næstved
  Odense
  Horsens
  Vejle
  Kolding
  """
```

